description:
The ninth collection. The red collection. This is art. This is satire.

This is one of the first "Art Satire" - Projects in the Cryptospace.

This "Renkert Snofla"-Collection again shows the development from the Basic Alfons Trekner without many effects to the final picture of this collection wich has lots of artefacts and effects.

8 Steps - 8 beautiful unique pictures.

Check out the details of the final version!

The way of creation is the artists secret.

This is the eighth collection of our negative Renkert Snofla. Others will follow. Maybe. Or not?! Every collection could be the final one!
name: Renkert Snofla - The ninth collection
